text: Loaded with a variety of shops and services. From supermarket Giant, bookshop, key duplicate shop, florist, clothes alteration, beauty shops, clinics, cafe., convenience stores , hardware shops.. you name it they surely got it.
My fast experience in beauty world MRT station.

Everytime I want to hike at Bukit Timah Hill, this station is the best station for me to go to. It is fun and convenient, with the old mall being a nice place to go to after the hike for refreshments.
Its one of the new stations in downtown line. Wide and spacious.

Very old building needs many improvement works done. most shops are for kid's learning. Piano, tuition, arts class, TCM, clinics, bakery. The only passenger lift is slow and always crowded and the escalator don't work most of the time. The roof top food court are full of hygiene problems. Dirty floors, serious birds nuisance.
